00:20:14.112 --> 00:20:16.314
&gt;&gt; It is mind boggling why.

00:20:16.314 --> 00:20:17.783
It makes no sense to me.

00:20:17.783 --> 00:20:20.619 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; David: Minister of Transport,
